《'''所願'''》（{{kor|k=소원|rm=So-won}}）是2013年上映的一部[[韩国电影|韩国电影]]，由[[李濬益|李濬益]]執导，[[薛景求|薛景求]]、[[严智苑|严智苑]]、[[李蕊_(韓國演員)|李蕊]]担任主演。<ref>{{cite web|last=Son|first=Jin-ah|title=Actors of ''Wish'' finally decided|url=http://en.starnnews.com/news/index.html?no=175847|work=StarN News|accessdate=2013-03-10|date=10 March 2013|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014172851/http://en.starnnews.com/news/index.html?no=175847|dead-url=no}}</ref>取材自2008年在韓國發生的'''[[趙斗淳事件|趙斗淳事件]]'''。以兒童性暴力為題材，講述家屬與其周圍人物在絕望之中為受害人治癒傷痛的故事。此案件也對政府施與壓力，承諾加重责罚。<ref>[http://chinese.joins.com/big5/article.do?method=detail&art_id=110605&category=003003 電影「夙願」票房突破200萬] {{Wayback|url=http://chinese.joins.com/big5/article.do?method=detail&art_id=110605&category=003003 |date=20190823053949 }} 韓國中央日報中文網</ref>该电影获得[[第34届韩国电影青龙奖|第34届韩国电影青龙奖]]最佳影片奖。<ref name=bd1>{{cite web|last=Jackson|first=Julie|title=''Wish'' snags three wins at Blue Dragon Film Awards|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20131124000202|work=[[The_Korea_Herald|The Korea Herald]]|accessdate=2014-03-25|date=24 November 2013|archive-date=2013-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131124132414/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20131124000202|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bd2>{{cite web|last=Yim|first=Seung-hye|title=Blue Dragon winner shocks|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2980931|work=[[中央日报_(韩国)|中央日报 (韩国)]]|accessdate=2014-03-25|date=25 November 2013|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917094333/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2980931|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bd3>{{cite web|last=Conran|first=Pierce|title=HOPE Scores Best Film at 34th Blue Dragon Awards|url=http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW&seq=2793|work=Korean Film Council|accessdate=2014-03-25|date=25 November 2013|archive-date=2011-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928122245/http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/news.jsp?mode=VIEW|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bd4>{{cite web|last=Cremin|first=Stephen|title=Hope wins through at Blue Dragon Awards|url=http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/hope-wins-through-at-blue-dragon-awards|work=亚洲电影资讯|accessdate=2014-03-24|date=25 November 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803032139/http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/hope-wins-through-at-blue-dragon-awards|archivedate=2014年8月3日}}</ref>

== 劇情簡介 ==
一個飄雨的早晨，小女孩素媛在上學路上遇到一個醉醺醺的大叔，被強行拉走，遭受了此生最不堪回首的傷害...這事件給她幼小的心靈和肉體造成難以抹滅的重創，同時，素媛的家庭也不得不承受來自社會各方的壓力與異樣眼光。然而，希望總在荊棘密佈後撥雲見日，在父母痛心之餘的關愛與扶持下，他們是否能幫素媛再次尋覓昔日笑顏，凝聚一家人重返生命的光和熱？

